## The 4ct Per-Carat Cliff: Why 3ct Is the Value Peak in Large Princess Cuts

The per-carat pricing progression in large princess diamonds reveals a structural pricing break between the 3ct range and 4ct+.

| Size | Grade | Price | Per Carat | vs 3ct Per-Carat |
|------|-------|-------|-----------|-----------------|
| 1ct G-VS2 | [View →](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/28961307?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | $2,212 | $2,212 | — |
